<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0013', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:199'>欽定四庫全書　　　　　經部二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='199:215'>　増修書説　　　　　　　書類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='215:221'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:247'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案増修書説三十五卷宋吕祖謙撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='247:270'>　　　　其門人時瀾増修通考云十卷趙希弁讀書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='270:293'>　　　　附志云六卷悉與此不合盖彼乃祖謙原書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='293:316'>　　　　未經時瀾所補者其時尚未成編傳鈔者隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='316:339'>　　　　意分卷故二家亦互異耳祖謙原書始洛誥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='339:365'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0013', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='365:388'>　　　　終秦誓其召誥以前堯典以後則門人雜記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='388:411'>　　　　之語録頗多俚俗瀾始刪潤其文成二十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='411:434'>　　　　卷又編定原書為十三卷合成是編王應麟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='434:457'>　　　　玉海稱林少穎書説至洛誥而終吕成公書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='457:480'>　　　　説自洛誥而始盖之奇受學于吕居仁祖謙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='480:503'>　　　　又受學于之奇本以終始其師説為一家之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='503:526'>　　　　學而瀾之所續則又終始祖謙一人之説也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='526:549'>　　　　瀾婺州清江人厲鶚宋詩紀事収其詩一篇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='549:575'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0013', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='575:598'>　　　　而不能舉其仕履考周必大平園集有祭瀾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='598:621'>　　　　文稱從政郎差充西外睦宗院宗學敎授而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='621:644'>　　　　瀾自序則稱以西邸文學入三山監丞盖作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='644:667'>　　　　是書時為監丞其後則以敎授終也吳師道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='667:690'>　　　　曰清江時鑄字夀卿吕成公同年進士與弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='690:713'>　　　　鋹率羣從弟子十餘人悉從公遊若澐若瀾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='713:736'>　　　　若涇尤時氏之秀成公輯書説瀾以平昔所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='736:760'>　　　　聞纂成之今所行書𫝊是也然則是書一名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='760:786'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0013', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='786:810'>　　　　為書𫝊矣又朱彞尊經義考是書三十五卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='810:833'>　　　　之外又别出時瀾増修書説三十卷並注曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='833:856'>　　　　存今三十卷者未見不知所據何本也乾隆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='856:871'>　　　　四十四年九月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='871:903'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
